{"tid":2291944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百年上水蘇格蘭軍徽，因新界東北計劃快將消失！","createTime":"2020-11-19T06:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:21:21.000Z","uid":384880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3e1c1cb8e81012cae246fcd5528987e550ea9d","tid":2291944,"uid":384880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"早前，上水一帶山火，令位於大石磨一座山岥上的軍徽，得以重見天日。<br />\n<br />\n此軍徽是1920年代，2nd Bn Scots Guards軍徽。是在這裡附近駐守的蘇格蘭近衛隊第二營，用石頭砌成。軍徽上分別寫了「2nd BATT」及「Scots Guards」。有著近百年的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，但因為政府發展東北計劃下，這座山將會發展成配水庫，以即意味，這有著百年歷史，代表著英軍守衛香港的遺跡，將會從此消失。<br />\n<br />\n今日可見，軍徽另一面山岥，已經有鏟泥車及工人開工，軍徽的上方及旁邊，亦插上了工程標記的旗仔。估計在未來數星期，軍徽便會被破壞。<br />\n<br />\n近年。香港人對本土歷史越來越有興趣，在多個紀念軍人及和平紀念日，亦越來越多港人參與有關活動。這一個代表著香港重要的歷史遺跡，就這麼草率被滅去，實感無奈及可惜。<br />\n<br />\n16/11/20<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/194035600634409/posts/3401828669855070/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F194035600634409%2Fposts%2F3401828669855070%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5iHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7ad9657d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/194035600634409/posts/3401828669855070/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdTNjAk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdTNjAk.jpg&h=1b61d4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFjAttJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFjAttJ.jpg&h=60e892f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日有人睇過仲未爛！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDWSvG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDWSvG8.jpg&h=876bfac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q9Tmo19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq9Tmo19.jpg&h=852b785a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">唔知救唔救到呢</span></strong></span>？！"},{"pid":"16f7b0ccd153a38d81e6ca4abb6971d814c285cd","tid":2291944,"uid":205377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"右上果個英係Bn ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係，會唔會係呢隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7udfaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7udfaX.jpg&h=5cd501d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f69f0b51980e851128990bfa0e7e46df6fc94c93","tid":2291944,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f7b0ccd153a38d81e6ca4abb6971d814c285cd","tid":2291944,"uid":205377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"右上果個英係Bn ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係，會唔會係呢隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7udfaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7udfaX.jpg&h=5cd501d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6d9f31e4aad4cc0d9f4b6d576dbf4fe5054912","tid":2291944,"uid":384880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}